{
  "stem": "13833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I learned Turkish terribly fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I still had my little Viennese dresses on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And because I spoke the language, I asked my parents whether I could go shopping for them, so they don't have to go.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one day, while I was in Turkish, shopping vegetables, a governess with a little boy came up to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she talked English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that time, I didn't speak English yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She said, you speak German?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, where are your parents?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, they are home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm shopping for them because I speak Turkish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So could we come home for you-- with you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they explained to my parents that in Turkey, they're still selling little girls into the harem.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And they shouldn't let me go alone because I was too beautiful a child.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's how we became friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The little boy's father was the president of Shell Corporation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was British, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from then on, they took care of me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they went everywhere with me, [LAUGHS] the governess and the little boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we both could see, from my house, that [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Charleston ?] was then starting to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after six months, we went home because it was very hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That time--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--came our Passovers there already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they, they thought that the radio is a spy business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Papi only could go in the evening to sell it because that was the only time they could speak.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a hard life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was most interesting for a seven-year-old child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people, the different people.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
